Interface AmbulanceChooser

public interface AmbulanceChooser

This interface represents ambulance chooser module. It is able to choose best ambulance able to resolve an incident.

Simon Busard

Method Detail

chooseBestAmbulance

int chooseBestAmbulance(int incidentInfoId,
                        java.util.LinkedList<java.lang.Integer> exclusionSet)
Return id of the best ambulance able to resolve incident designated by incidentInfoId id. It do not take ambulances in exclusionSet into account. If no ambulance is found, -1 is returned.

Precondition:
incidentInfoId id of the incident exclusionSet set of ids of ambulances not to take into account
Postcondition
return id of the best ambulance or -1 if no such ambulance is found
